channel.description:
Yeah, as BMchatFags would know I get all 4 of my Wisdom Teeth pulled on Thursday morning (the 24th).
I think it was Viv who told me to post before and after pics. So here is the before in ultra scene-bathroommirror-esque style pics.
Sex [img]https://img684.imageshack.us/img684/1079/sspx9483.jpg[/img] A little closer... [img]https://img190.imageshack.us/img190/3850/sspx9484.jpg[/img]
After images coming...after the teeth actually get pulled

item.title: Wisdom Teeth...
item.dc:creator: Elpants
item.description:
Teeth are out, I guess each tooth was abnormally large and had 4 roots instead of 3, so it was a little tough getting them out. The top left tooth had a root break off and start receding into my sinuses and my Dentist said he was lucky to be able to fish it out.


I guess I got lucky with minimal swelling.

But I guess the pancakes were pretty bloody…
